            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ulpi<lb break="no" n="2"/>us <lb n="3"/>Silva<lb break="no" n="4"/>nus <lb n="5"/>fac<lb break="no" n="6"/>tus <lb n="7"/>Arau<lb break="no" n="8"/>sione <lb n="9"/>emeri<lb break="no" n="10"/>tus <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/>II <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="12"/>votum <lb n="13"/>solvit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Relief: Mithras tötet den Stier. Die Fackelträger Cautes und Cautopates sind dabei. Im Vordergrund: Hund, Schlang, Skorpion und vielleicht Rabe.</p>
